data.description: Amazing location walking distance to schools, large driveway for multiple cars. big and finished garage. spacious master bedroom with a walk-in closet. Large kitchen, deck. gleaming hardwood floors, very dry basement with special T French drain system and upgraded waterproofing system 1 ft below foundation all around house a must see to appreciate, upgraded electric to 200 amp, finished attic a must see, seller will leave house furnished if buyer wants very expensive Italina furniture, 4 exits or entrances to house. Docking rights with house, walk to Newbridge Park with pools and ice skating rink and more,  Very unique house a must see to appreciate...
